{"id": 672, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的密码是什么？", "description": "我知道要有安全意识，但每个网站用不一样的密码？我会死。", "record_count": 4018, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183517NPJ5AzRaBG2WHkXs.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-01T11:17:40Z", "options": [{"id": 35329, "content": "123456789", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370121}, {"id": 31746, "content": "七八个常用密码的排列组合吧……万一忘了猜起来也比较容易……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340271}, {"id": 30725, "content": "生日呗，然后加上自己名字缩写，哎呀，怎么说出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 30981, "content": "密码管理软件是个好帮手，技术改变生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155699}, {"id": 32006, "content": "我的密码是一串毫无意义的数字", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341796}, {"id": 32774, "content": "好想回一句 你猜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346428}, {"id": 30728, "content": "初恋的名字，太习惯了一直没改过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 230483}, {"id": 31240, "content": "该网站简称加上通用后缀，那个名字加幸运数字组成的通用后缀我用了十几年了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 30729, "content": "自己的名字（全拼或者简拼）加短号（深圳短号）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335706}, {"id": 30730, "content": "潇洒的古诗拼音。前半句或后半句。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188341}, {"id": 30731, "content": "认识一个同学用某视频链接的数字做密码。。比如爱奇艺里甄嬛传第三集的链接那种╮(╯▽╰)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60125}, {"id": 30988, "content": "三套有自己规律的密码来回切换", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336612}, {"id": 31756, "content": "手机随机验证码，拯救密码健忘群体", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340315}, {"id": 37903, "content": "永远只有一个密码或它的演变", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340106}, {"id": 34321, "content": "某人的生日日期和名字缩写字母。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360210}, {"id": 34577, "content": "有对象的对象名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335094}, {"id": 30738, "content": "圆周率，斐波那契数列，e值都有，每个地方用一个，再加上几个符号和字母。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328516}, {"id": 30740, "content": "cptbtptpbcptdtptp吃葡萄不吐葡萄皮，不吃葡萄倒吐葡萄皮", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004729rx15S7atBiD3JLqh.jpg", "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 221586}, {"id": 32788, "content": "自己记不住的密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346512}, {"id": 40468, "content": "zg761994-", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260718}, {"id": 30741, "content": "一句话而且只有自己理解什么意思??", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232534}, {"id": 30998, "content": "键盘上的特殊字符", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336643}, {"id": 32024, "content": "123456", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334982}, {"id": 30745, "content": "常用的是三组密码，社交类、网银类、简单快速登录类", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335781}, {"id": 32282, "content": "多任女朋友的生日…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343448}, {"id": 47130, "content": "初中时灵机一动随便写了一串数字并强迫自己背下来当做原始密码，日后所有的社交钱包都是原始密码＋名字（或小名）缩写+标点符号！哈哈哈(ღˇ◡ˇღ)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 56389}, {"id": 32795, "content": "字母数字穿插", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346455}, {"id": 34588, "content": "男友名字缩写 所有网站都是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363143}, {"id": 31006, "content": 